name: Remember Me, i love you but aim... 21+
description: Since being born until the age of 22 this year, it has been a long journey and twists and turns. But, the journey that I haven't tasted is love, indeed there is a lot of love coming, but for some reason this heart is very cold to begin with. Of all the love that comes, only your love starts to warm this frozen heart until it melts. But remember, this heart doesn't fully love you, because I'm not sure whether you will accept my sadness for the past 21 years. Remember me, I love you but... 21+
